# ✅ Test Case: TC001_LoginFunctionality_ValidCredentials

**Title**: Verify user can log in successfully with valid credentials  
**Module**: User Authentication  
**Author**: Aicha Moustatia  
**Date Executed**: 2025-06-10  
**Priority**: High  
**Status**: ✅ Passed

---

## 🔍 Test Scenario
Verify that a user can successfully log in with valid credentials.

---

## 📌 Preconditions
- User is on the login page  
- User has a valid username: `Admin`  
- Password: `Test@1234`  

---

## 🧪 Test Steps & Results

| Step | Action                     | Expected Result                          | Actual Result                         | Status |
|------|-----------------------------|-------------------------------------------|----------------------------------------|--------|
| 1    | Navigate to login page      | Login page loads successfully             | Login page loaded                      | ✅     |
| 2    | Enter valid username        | Username field accepts input              | Input accepted                         | ✅     |
| 3    | Enter valid password        | Password field accepts input              | Input accepted                         | ✅     |
| 4    | Click "Login" button        | User redirected to dashboard              | Redirect successful                     | ✅     |

---

## ✅ Final Result
**Passed** — user successfully logged in and redirected to dashboard.

## 🧾 Notes
- Browser: Chrome v123  
- OS: Windows 11  
- Test performed on staging environment: `staging.testsite.com`  
